OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,FFrench company, Engie, has announced
OL,7,Fit has agreed a deal to purchase
OL,8,Felectricity distributor, UK Power
OL,9,FNetworks (UKPN).
OL,11,FThe company supplies power across
OL,12,FKent, Sussex, London, and the East of
OL,13,FEngland, to more than 8.5million
OL,14,Fpeople.
OL,16,FEngie agreed to buy UKPN for
OL,17,F#10.5billion from its current owners,
OL,18,FCK Infrastructure Holdings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
