PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,FThe deal is likely to complete by mid-
OL,7,F2026 following regulatory approval,
OL,8,FEngie said.
OL,10,FThe purchase of UKPN is part of
OL,11,Fefforts by the French utility giant to
OL,12,Frebalance the way it works, focusing
OL,13,Fon 'regulated electricity networks'.
OL,15,FIt is also part of efforts to
OL,16,Fstrengthen the company's footprint in
OL,17,Fthe UK, which is a key country for
OL,18,FEngie going forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
