FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,FEngie has had a presence in the UK for
OL,7,Fsome time. Until 2020, Engie was a
OL,8,Fdomestic power supplier, with 70,000
OL,9,Fcustomers. They were later transferred
OL,10,Fto Octopus.
OL,12,FIt has continued to deal with business
OL,13,Fcustomers, and has a presence in
OL,14,Fcities including Southampton, where it
OL,15,Foperates the Southampton District
OL,16,FEnergy Scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
