OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,FCatherine MacGregor, Engie CEO, said:
OL,7,F"The acquisition of UKPN represents a
OL,8,Fdecisive step in strengthening ENGIE's
OL,9,Fposition as the best energy transition
OL,10,Futility.
OL,12,F"It is fully aligned with our ambition
OL,13,Fto become a key player in regulated
OL,14,Felectricity network infrastructures,
OL,15,Fwhich are essential for energy
OL,16,Fsecurity, demand electrification and
OL,17,Fgreater system flexibility. This
OL,18,Ftransaction will both enhance the
OL,19,FGroup's growth trajectory and reduce
OL,20,Four risk profile, providing more
OL,21,Fvisibility on future earnings.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
