FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,F"It also enables us to reinforce our
OL,7,Fposition in the United Kingdom, a key
OL,8,Fcountry with a stable regulatory
OL,9,Fframework and clear decarbonisation
OL,10,Ftargets. We are proud to join forces
OL,11,Fwith UKPN's talented teams as we
OL,12,Fembark on this new chapter together.>
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eo]
