CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,FBasil Scarsella, UK Power Networks
OL,7,FCEO, said: "This transaction marks an
OL,8,Fimportant milestone in the history of
OL,9,FUKPN and for all its employees. By
OL,10,Fjoining ENGIE, we continue to be part
OL,11,Fof a global energy leader with the
OL,12,Ffinancial strength, industrial
OL,13,Fcapabilities, and long-term vision to
OL,14,Fsupport our next phase of development.
OL,16,F"UKPN (now) embarks on a period of
OL,17,Fsignificant investment in our network
OL,18,Fto enable economic growth in London,
OL,19,Fthe South East, and East of England.
OL,26,@oD@LOUxD@GpmxD@Kpn
