PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772125457
OL,3,CFrench utility giant buys UK Power
OL,4,CNetworks in #10billion deal
OL,6,F"It will reinforce our ability to
OL,7,Fserve our 8.5 million customers with
OL,8,Fthe highest standards of safety,
OL,9,Fcustomer service, and reliability. We
OL,10,Fshare ENGIE's strategic ambition and
OL,11,Fvalues and are excited to embark on
OL,12,Fthis new chapter together, ensuring a
OL,13,Fsmooth transition for our teams and
OL,14,Fcontinued excellent service for the
OL,15,Fcommunities we serve."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@VO]
